  "title": "fix(answers): mark as deprecated",
  "body": "While the answers feature still works, it no longer has any difference from a regular search, and therefore no longer needs its own specialised widget.\r\n\r\nEven though it's marked as experimental, I still don't think it's a good idea to delete without major version, as it's used in the downstream packages",
